<h2 id="scope">1 Scope</h2>
<p>This standard defines how FLAC bitstreams shall be mapped in the MXF Generic Container (SMPTE 379M).</p>
<p>This standard maps the FLAC encoded Audio packets as either frame-wrapped or clip-wrapped using the mechanisms defined in SMPTE 379M.</p>
<p>This standard defines the KLV coding, the Essence Container Universal Label, the Essence Compression Universal Label and the Essence Descriptor to be used when wrapping FLAC bitstreams in the MXF Generic Container.</p>
